    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Holiday-Tribute-Gifts-Programs-Facebook.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-18616\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Holiday-Tribute-Gifts-Programs-Facebook-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"Basic RGB\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Holiday-Tribute-Gifts-Programs-Facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Holiday-Tribute-Gifts-Programs-Facebook.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Holiday-Tribute-Gifts-Programs-Facebook.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Holiday-Tribute-Gifts-Programs-Facebook.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Holiday-Tribute-Gifts-Programs-Facebook.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>For environmentally friendly and socially conscious holiday shoppers that prefer to give donations to nonprofits as holiday gifts, the 10 holiday tribute gift programs listed below are a good starting point for your holiday shopping. Ranging from wildlife conservation to refugee relief, tribute gifts make excellent holiday gifts for friends, family, and work colleagues. If you prefer to give traditional gifts, you can also shop for good at <strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2015/11/01/27-online-stores-that-benefit-nonprofits/\">27 online stores that benefit nonprofits</a></strong>. Either way, put your consumer spending power to work fostering social good this holiday season.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. CARE Packages<br />\n<a href=\"http://gifts.care.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18584\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/button_shop_now-roounded.jpg?resize=82%2C22\" alt=\"button_shop_now roounded\" width=\"82\" height=\"22\" /></a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://gifts.care.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18590\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/CARE.png?resize=600%2C278\" alt=\"CARE\" width=\"600\" height=\"278\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/CARE.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/CARE.png?resize=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Defenders of Wildlife Adoption Center<br />\n<a href=\"https://secure.defenders.org/site/SPageNavigator/wagc_homepage.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18584\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/button_shop_now-roounded.jpg?resize=82%2C22\" alt=\"button_shop_now roounded\" width=\"82\" height=\"22\" /></a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://secure.defenders.org/site/SPageNavigator/wagc_homepage.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18597\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Defenders-of-Wildlife.png?resize=600%2C270\" alt=\"Defenders of Wildlife\" width=\"600\" height=\"270\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Defenders-of-Wildlife.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Defenders-of-Wildlife.png?resize=300%2C135&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. Elephant Sanctuary in Tennessee Adoptions<br />\n<a href=\"http://shop.elephants.com/product/43E6178/supportanelephant.php\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18584\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/button_shop_now-roounded.jpg?resize=82%2C22\" alt=\"button_shop_now roounded\" width=\"82\" height=\"22\" /></a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://shop.elephants.com/product/43E6178/supportanelephant.php\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18610\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Adopt.png?resize=600%2C344\" alt=\"Adopt\" width=\"600\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Adopt.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Adopt.png?resize=300%2C172&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. International Rescue Committee Rescue Gifts<br />\n<a href=\"http://gifts.rescue.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18584\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/button_shop_now-roounded.jpg?resize=82%2C22\" alt=\"button_shop_now roounded\" width=\"82\" height=\"22\" /></a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://gifts.rescue.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18588\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Rescue-Gifts.png?resize=600%2C355\" alt=\"Rescue Gifts\" width=\"600\" height=\"355\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Rescue-Gifts.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Rescue-Gifts.png?resize=300%2C178&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. National Audubon Society Adoption Catalog<br />\n<a href=\"https://secure.audubon.org/site/SPageNavigator/2014_Adoption_Catalog_Homepage.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18584\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/button_shop_now-roounded.jpg?resize=82%2C22\" alt=\"button_shop_now roounded\" width=\"82\" height=\"22\" /></a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://secure.audubon.org/site/SPageNavigator/2014_Adoption_Catalog_Homepage.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18594\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/audubon-society.png?resize=600%2C361\" alt=\"audubon society\" width=\"600\" height=\"361\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/audubon-society.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/audubon-society.png?resize=300%2C181&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. Nothing But Nets Gift Nets<br />\n<a href=\"https://secure.globalproblems-globalsolutions.org/site/SPageNavigator/nbn_api_form.html?form_id=9020\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18584\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/button_shop_now-roounded.jpg?resize=82%2C22\" alt=\"button_shop_now roounded\" width=\"82\" height=\"22\" /></a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://secure.globalproblems-globalsolutions.org/site/SPageNavigator/nbn_api_form.html?form_id=9020\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18593\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Nothing-But-Nets.png?resize=600%2C466\" alt=\"Nothing But Nets\" width=\"600\" height=\"466\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Nothing-But-Nets.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Nothing-But-Nets.png?resize=300%2C233&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">7. Oxfam Unwrapped Catalog<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.oxfamamericaunwrapped.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18584\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/button_shop_now-roounded.jpg?resize=82%2C22\" alt=\"button_shop_now roounded\" width=\"82\" height=\"22\" /></a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.oxfamamericaunwrapped.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18599\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Oxfam-Unwrapped.png?resize=600%2C278\" alt=\"Oxfam Unwrapped\" width=\"600\" height=\"278\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Oxfam-Unwrapped.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Oxfam-Unwrapped.png?resize=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. Save the Children Gifts of Joy<br />\n<a href=\"http://gift.savethechildren.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18584\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/button_shop_now-roounded.jpg?resize=82%2C22\" alt=\"button_shop_now roounded\" width=\"82\" height=\"22\" /></a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://gift.savethechildren.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18607\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Save-the-Children.png?resize=600%2C351\" alt=\"Save the Children\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Save-the-Children.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Save-the-Children.png?resize=300%2C176&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. Wilderness Society Adoption Catalog<br />\n<a href=\"https://secure.wilderness.org/site/Ecommerce?store_id=4201\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18584\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/button_shop_now-roounded.jpg?resize=82%2C22\" alt=\"button_shop_now roounded\" width=\"82\" height=\"22\" /></a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://secure.wilderness.org/site/Ecommerce?store_id=4201\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18586\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Wlderness-Society.png?resize=600%2C341\" alt=\"Wlderness Society\" width=\"600\" height=\"341\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Wlderness-Society.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Wlderness-Society.png?resize=300%2C171&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">10. World Vision Gift Catalog<br />\n<a href=\"http://donate.worldvision.org/ways-to-give/gift-catalog\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18584\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/button_shop_now-roounded.jpg?resize=82%2C22\" alt=\"button_shop_now roounded\" width=\"82\" height=\"22\" /></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://donate.worldvision.org/ways-to-give/gift-catalog\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18576\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/World-Vision.png?resize=600%2C388\" alt=\"World Vision\" width=\"600\" height=\"388\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/World-Vision.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/World-Vision.png?resize=300%2C194&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" src=\" http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/mobile-for-good-with-ribbon.jpg\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n",
